        {
            "title": "黑期高水逾60點 重磅港股ADR普遍升",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">外圍股市持續反彈，再度支持港股氣氛。新加坡黑期於今早約8時16分升106點或0.5%，報21480點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股ADR指數報21492點，較香港上日現貨收市高74點或0.35%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合港幣457.9元，較上日香港收市高3.93元或0.87%；阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合港幣110.5元，較上日香港收市高2.28元或2.11%</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美團(03690)ADR收市折合港幣145元，較上日香港收市低0.88元或0.6%；京東(09618)ADR收市折合港幣148元，較上日香港收市高1.44元或0.98%；小米(01810)ADR收市折合港幣43.2元，較上日香港收市低0.02元或0.05%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：騰訊官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滙控(00005)ADR收市折合港幣79.2元，較上日香港收市高0.66元或0.84%；友邦(01299)ADR收市折合港幣52.3元，較上日香港收市高0.15元或0.28%；港交所(00388)ADR收市折合港幣337.3元，較上日香港收市高3.26元或0.98%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國平安(02318)ADR收市折合港幣43.6元，較上日香港收市低0.18元或0.41%；建設銀行(00939)ADR收市折合港幣6.6元，較上日香港收市高0.01元或0.17%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指夜市期指收報21585點，升169點，較上日恒指收市21417點，高水168點。科指期貨夜市收報5063點，較上日科指收市高水48點；國指期貨夜市收報8026點，較上日國指收市高水60點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14855145-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e9%ab%98%e6%b0%b4%e9%80%be60%e9%bb%9e-%e9%87%8d%e7%a3%85%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1adr%e6%99%ae%e9%81%8d%e5%8d%87",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/ADR-1_source-bp_-2-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-15 08:25:43",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
